# Fixture auto-export (`bench export-fixtures`) writes files using Frappe's
# default doctype_snake_case.json naming, ignoring our prefixed canonical
# filenames. The unprefixed files duplicate the prefixed ones and would
# dirty the tree. See CLAUDE.md "Fixture auto-export gotcha" for details.
dux_civil_works/fixtures/uom.json
dux_civil_works/fixtures/item_group.json
dux_civil_works/fixtures/item.json
dux_civil_works/fixtures/property_setter.json
